🔄 How Renewals Work

This part is elegant.

EXPIRY REMINDER

Before expiry:

Your scheduled worker checks:

GET /subscriptions

Finds subscriptions expiring soon.

Then:

send webhook to T2Mobile
T2Mobile collects payment
AFTER PAYMENT

T2Mobile calls fulfilment again.

But this time:
you do NOT create new subscription.

Instead:
you extend existing one.

Zoho supports:

POST /subscriptions/{id}/extend

🔥 THAT Is Probably Renewal Provisioning

Meaning:

existing subscription
      ↓
extend billing cycles
      ↓
new expiry date
