🚨 VERY Important Discovery

Zoho has TWO provisioning models mentioned in docs:

1. Reseller/Partner-managed mode

Partner provisions on behalf of customers.

2. Subscription API mode

Customer self-manages.

Your T2Mobile architecture clearly matches:

Partner/Reseller Purchase Mode

because:

T2Mobile owns payment
Icontech provisions on behalf of customer
customer does not directly buy from Zoho
